Revision history for Perl extension Tk::CanvasDirTree.

0.01  Wed Apr  5  2006
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-AXn Tk::CanvasDirTree

0.02  Wed Apr 12, 2006
       - made background image scroll automatically to give appearance
            of a stationary background ( optional with -floatback=>1 ) 
       - fixed a possible memory leak due to image rebuilding

0.03  Wed Apr 12, 2006
       - small documentation fixes 
       - added demo for floating background    